Preconditions:

2.被测板子正常启动
TestSteps:

AS_Strg_Angle_Req=-3000/0/3553.5
AS_Strg_WorkMode_Req=0/1/2/3/4/5/6
AS_Strg0_Enable=0/1/2/3
AS_Steering_torque_superposition=-12.8/0/12.7
AS_Strg_Spd_Req=0/2550
AS_Strg1_Enable=0/1/2/3
AS_Strg_Life_Signal=0/15

AS_Steering_torque_superposition=-12.8/0/12.7
